# claudit scrub denylist — EXAMPLE. Copy to ~/.claude/claudit/scrub.txt and edit.
#
# Add any names the regex scrubbers can't know about: your company / org, Azure or Entra
# tenant names, client names, internal hostnames, project codenames, people's names, etc.
# Each non-comment line is redacted (whole-word, case-insensitive) to [REDACTED] before any
# issue is posted. Keep this list LOCAL — do not commit your real names to a public repo.

# AcmeCorp
# Acme Corporation
# contoso          # an Entra tenant name
# build-server-01  # an internal hostname
# Jane Doe         # a teammate's name
